{"tid":1388733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人：談，大門敞開；打，奉陪到底","createTime":"2019-07-30T18:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T01:19:48.000Z","uid":286864,"like":277,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"5b01eae8bd41fc860ebc2dc5fb8d743759e5d1aa","tid":1388733,"uid":286864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:15:05.000Z","msg":"對於中共發起的戰爭，香港人早就表明態度：不願打，但也不怕打，必要時不得不打。面對中共的軟硬兩手，香港人也早已給出答案。<br />\n<br />\n經歷了香港開埠百多年風風雨雨的香港人，什麽樣的陣勢沒見過？在實現民主自由的偉大進程中，必然會有艱難險阻甚至驚濤駭浪。<br />\n<br />\n中共發起的全面侵略和統戰，不過是香港發展進程中的一道坎兒，沒什麽大不了，香港必將堅定信心、迎難而上，化危為機，鬥出一片新天地。<br />\n<br />\n無論外部風雲如何變幻，對香港來說，最重要的就是做好自己的事情，不斷進步，全面抗爭，實現真正高質量的民主發展。<br />\n<br />\n中共下一步是要談，還是要打，抑或是採取別的動作，香港人都已做好了全面應對的準備。<br />\n<br />\n這正如香港人所指出，中國經濟不是一片大海，而是一個小池塘，需要的是香港這一個獨特的入海口；狂風暴雨可以掀翻小池塘，唯有依靠入海口，才能從外引入養份，不至於封鎖自毀；經歷了無數次狂風驟雨，香港這個入海口也會依舊在那兒，而若然上天要香港滅亡，中共也會一起陪葬。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">IF WE BURN, YOU BURN WITH US</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"eb8a6dc73f61fcb00b0b3eb097e4f966b5679117","tid":1388733,"uid":108337,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:15:59.000Z","msg":"不願打，但也不怕打，必要時不得不打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f55249a676eab0f088d6cd80e912fe7451166b4","tid":1388733,"uid":242724,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:16:39.000Z","msg":"好撚正!"},{"pid":"5887e6913c2c461e1790586cd52753829c1b74bd","tid":1388733,"uid":30688,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:17:36.000Z","msg":"寫得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵人share上乜鳩we七，微博<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8143863ad91ca040ce547430479cb62f6b646c","tid":1388733,"uid":290885,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:20:40.000Z","msg":"談？要講一早講曬  不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f538ea1c8a4088dde1428bdc16a8a11e4fdfb66","tid":1388733,"uid":39181,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:21:23.000Z","msg":"香港人爭取民主既決心係堅定不疑的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c099b88bce0e5efe592bc3ab8088732c4af20323","tid":1388733,"uid":286864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:24:46.000Z","msg":"香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b4c2bc2ba158e4bacd05c1e96ea7c2a93dfa92","tid":1388733,"uid":187755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:28:02.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"060c32a742b3d1fce462e19ce13f49531d5ddb6f","tid":1388733,"uid":151256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:28:31.000Z","msg":"有乜好談<br />\n五大訴求講哂出嚟"},{"pid":"44fa2f5eb0cf8b22452de20206a1c17b92be2fb4","tid":1388733,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a8143863ad91ca040ce547430479cb62f6b646c","tid":1388733,"uid":290885,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:20:40.000Z","msg":"談？要講一早講曬  不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:29:42.000Z","msg":"你要傾，同我滿足哂五大訴求再講，不排除加埋你自己新整果D"},{"pid":"6419d7041fd141e23e8763d194a00105d503ea3e","tid":1388733,"uid":295187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:31:56.000Z","msg":"各位手足要堅持 不退讓 記得我地點解要行出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef66824911d3f86ef4485eeccdf59f8678df29b3","tid":1388733,"uid":6111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:37:31.000Z","msg":"依次輸左好多人會被清算<br />\n比人抄左牌果d係最大機會<br />\n即使明知係捱打都要出去<br />\n因為我地冇得再輸"},{"pid":"b944264df6c614b80bd41c99b9e4572fb52633e9","tid":1388733,"uid":286864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T23:17:46.000Z","msg":"香港加油<img src=\"/as